"Invalid input JSON on line 1, column 106: Cannot build FormSubmissionValue, some of required attributes are not set [name, value]"

The fields have a nmae and a value based on the form data in HubSpot. Can tou check if the way I am structuring the data is correct based on what it is expecting?

```axios
                .post('<https://api.hsforms.com/submissions/v3/integration/submit/8191872/c131b7e7-f5fe-494f-9302-41b2e50dc022>', {
                    fields: [{
                        firstname: 'a name here',
                        lastname: 'a surname here',
                        company: 'TMA',
                        email: '<mailto:test@test.com|test@test.com>'

                    }]               
                },
                )
                .then(response =&gt; {


                })
                .catch(error =&gt; {

                    console.log(error);
                    debugger;
                })
                .then(response =&gt; {

                });```
