Chris

Hey <@U01FD72A54Z> the fields array should look like this:
```  "fields": [
    {
      "name": "email",
      "value": "<mailto:example@example.com|example@example.com>"
    },
    {
      "name": "firstname",
      "value": "Jeff"
    }
  ],```
Per <https://legacydocs.HubSpot.com/docs/methods/forms/submit_form|the docs>
